 6. the person eating pomegranate is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person eating potato is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 8. the malaysian is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person eating lemon is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

